    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《凶寓》是一款第一人称写实风格的怪谈类型中式恐怖游戏。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家将体验极致的压抑与恐怖氛围，精心设计的恐怖点，90年代中式氛围，神秘惊悚扭曲的不明实体生物。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>剧情介绍:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>玩家将扮演一位户外探险频道的视频主，收到粉丝的付费邀约来到一栋发生过集体失踪案的公寓进行调查拍摄。而本身无神论的主角将会在这里遭遇超出他认知的恐怖事件。</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>动态展示</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114900/extras/c2bec32fc49865235837f1bd1ef00723.poster.avif?t=1769510435\" width=600 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114900/extras/c2bec32fc49865235837f1bd1ef00723.webm?t=1769510435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114900/extras/c2bec32fc49865235837f1bd1ef00723.mp4?t=1769510435\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114900/extras/ab9574fd4b8dfb75f3574ae70405679a.poster.avif?t=1769510435\" width=600 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114900/extras/ab9574fd4b8dfb75f3574ae70405679a.webm?t=1769510435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114900/extras/ab9574fd4b8dfb75f3574ae70405679a.mp4?t=1769510435\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114900/extras/d8ff5e2161f85f0dae202e3c4dee9ba8.poster.avif?t=1769510435\" width=600 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/311